{# PV modules. `variant` picks the asset AND dictates where the caller places it:
   `full` = the roof array, laid flush in the slope ; `kit` = the two-module
   plug-and-play frame, which stands on the GROUND (garden/balcony) — no
   installer, no working at height, that is the whole point of a kit.
   The glint animates on producing days (scene.css) in both variants. #}
{% props variant = 'full' %}
<g class="solar solar--{{ variant }}"{{ attributes }}>{{ include(variant == 'kit' ? 'game/scene/assets/solar-kit.svg' : 'game/scene/assets/solar-panels.svg') }}</g>
